    </div>
    <div class="space-item">
      <div class="space-icon">üè¢</div>
      <div class="space-name">Commercial Spaces</div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-item">
      <div class="space-icon">üåø</div>
      <div class="space-name">Outdoor & Terrace</div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-item">
      <div class="space-icon">üöó</div>
      <div class="space-name">Garage Floors</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq">
  <div class="stag reveal">FAQ</div>
  <h2 class="reveal">Common Questions</h2>
  <div class="faq-list reveal">
    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary>Does the price include tiles?</summary>
      <p>No ‚Äî Rs. 350/sq.ft is labour only. You purchase your preferred tiles and we handle all installation materials (adhesive, grout, leveling clips).</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How long does a typical floor tiling job take?</summary>
      <p>A standard bedroom (150‚Äì200 sq.ft) typically takes one full day. Larger areas are phased to allow for curing time between sections.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can you tile over existing tiles?</summary>
      <p>Yes, in most cases. We assess the existing surface first ‚Äî if the existing tiles are firmly bonded and level, overlay tiling is a viable option and avoids demolition costs.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What is the minimum curing time before walking on the floor?</summary>
      <p>We recommend 24 hours before light foot traffic and 48 hours before furniture is moved in. Full adhesive cure is achieved at 72 hours.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do you provide a guarantee on workmanship?</summary>
      <p>Yes. We stand behind every job. If any tiles lift or grout cracks within the first 12 months due to workmanship, we will rectify it at no charge.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ‚îÄ‚îÄ Overview ‚îÄ‚îÄ */

  .overview {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .7rem;
    margin-top: .5rem;
  }

  .check-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: .75rem;
    font-size: .9rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: '‚óÜ';
    font-size: .42rem;
    color: var(--clay);
    margin-top: .4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .price-card {
    background: var(--sand);
    padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .price-card.accent {
    background: var(--charcoal);
  }

  .pc-label {
    font-size: .65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }

  .accent .pc-label { color: rgba(245,240,232,.45); }

  .pc-price {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--clay);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .pc-unit {
    font-size: .78rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    margin-top: .25rem;
    margin-bottom: .8rem;
  }

  .accent .pc-unit { color: rgba(245,240,232,.4); }

  .pc-note {
    font-size: .78rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    padding-top: .75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }

  .accent .pc-note {
    color: rgba(245,240,232,.5);
    border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }

  .price-note {
    font-size: .75rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ‚îÄ‚îÄ Tile Sizes ‚îÄ‚îÄ */

  .tile-sizes {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .tile-sizes h2 { color: var(--cream); }
  .tile-sizes .sdesc { color: rgba(245,240,232,.45); }

  .size-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .size-card {
    background: #211c18;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color .25s;
  }

  .size-card:hover { border-color: rgba(196,120,74,.4); }

  .size-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--clay);
  }

  .size-dim {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--clay);
    margin-bottom: .4rem;
  }

  .size-label {
    font-size: .75rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,.4);
  }

  .size-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(196,120,74,.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,120,74,.3);
    color: var(--clay);
    font-size: .6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    padding: .15rem .55rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: .6rem;
  }

  /* ‚îÄ‚îÄ Process ‚îÄ‚îÄ */

  .process {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step {
    padding: 1.8rem;
    background: var(--off-white);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--stone);
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: border-color .2s;
  }

  .step:hover { border-color: var(--clay); }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--stone);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: .7rem;
  }

  .step-name {
    font-size: .9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: .8rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ‚îÄ‚îÄ Spaces ‚îÄ‚îÄ */

  .spaces {
    background: var(--sand);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .spaces-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .space-item {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
    padding: 1.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--stone);
    transition: border-color .2s;
  }

  .space-item:hover { border-color: var(--clay); }

  .space-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }

  .space-name {
    font-size: .75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* ‚îÄ‚îÄ FAQ ‚îÄ‚îÄ */

  .faq {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 720px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .6rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid var(--stone);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem;
    font-size: .9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--clay);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '‚àí'; }

  .faq-item p {
    padding: 0 1.4rem 1.1rem;
    font-size: .85rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ‚îÄ‚îÄ Responsive ‚îÄ‚îÄ */

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .overview, .tile-sizes, .process, .spaces, .faq {
      padding-left: 2.5rem;
      padding-right: 2.5rem;
    }

    .overview { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .size-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .steps { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .spaces-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .overview, .tile-sizes, .process, .spaces, .faq {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .size-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .spaces-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
